<td>
<p><a href="/wiki/Literary_criticism" title="Literary criticism">Criticism</a><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <strong class="selflink">Theory</strong><span style="font-weight:bold;">&#160;·</span> <a href="/wiki/Literary_magazine" title="Literary magazine">Magazines</a></p>
</td>
